to security in the event of unemployment, sickness, disability, widowhood, old
age or other lack of livelihood in circumstances beyond his control.<EOS> (2)
Motherhood and childhood are entitled to special care and assistance.<EOS> All
children, whether born in or out of wedlock, shall enjoy the same social
